node.text:
💦 Summer in Alaska. Would you like to dive into this cold and fresh water?

Credits: @johnderting.

Songs: 
1. In The End - @mellen_gi & @tommeeprofitt.

2. Sing me to Sleep - @alanwalkermusic.

3. Roses - @saintjhn & @imanbekmusic.
